HEADWORD: Clementine
<hw>Clem"ent*ine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to Clement, esp. to St. Clement of Rome and the spurious homilies
attributed to him, or to Pope Clement V. and his compilations of canon
law.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

